Package: margEVT
Type: Package
Title: Marginalization for Non-Homogeneous Extreme Value Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Rodrigo Fonseca", "Villa", email = "rodrigo03.villa@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-2938-2270"))
Description: Fits non-homogeneous point process models for extreme value
    analysis via penalized maximum likelihood with elastic-net regularization.
    Computes unconditional return levels by marginalizing over arbitrary
    time-varying covariates, using conditional scenarios, parametric
    stochastic simulation, or empirical block bootstrap.
